/-- Tensoring over the adele ring is the same as the product of tensoring over в„қ and
the restricted product of tensoring over в„ҡвӮҡ. -/
noncomputable def IntegralLattice.tensorAdelesContinuousEquivRestrictedProduct :
    (IntegralLattice в„Ө в„ҡ V) вҠ—[в„Ө] AdeleRing (рқ“һ в„ҡ) в„ҡ вүғL[в„Ө]
    ((IntegralLattice в„Ө в„ҡ V) вҠ—[в„Ө] InfiniteAdeleRing в„ҡ) Г—
    (О Кі v : IsDedekindDomain.HeightOneSpectrum (рқ“һ в„ҡ),
      [(IntegralLattice в„Ө в„ҡ V) вҠ—[в„Ө] v.adicCompletion в„ҡ,
        (LinearMap.range (LinearMap.lTensor (IntegralLattice в„Ө в„ҡ V)
          (v.adicCompletionIntegers в„ҡ).toIntSubmodule.subtype))]) := {
  __ := IntegralLattice.tensorAdelesEquivRestrictedProduct V
  /-
